{"title":"Transfer Entropy 기반 IMV-LSTM을 활용한 CH₄ Flux 예측","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Transfer Entropy 기반 IMV-LSTM을 활용한 CH₄ Flux 예측","date":"2026-04-10","author":"Prof. Shin (phyzik)","categories":["인과추론","딥러닝","시계열","Python"],"image":"thumbnail.png","description":"Transfer Entropy를 변수 선택 기준으로 활용하여 IMV-LSTM 아키텍처에 통합하는 방법을 소개합니다.\nFLUXNET CH₄ 데이터에 적용하여 인과 구조 기반 예측 성능을 검증합니다.\n"},"headingText":"개요","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\nTransfer Entropy(TE)는 정보이론 기반의 비선형 인과성 측도입니다.\n\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef transfer_entropy(X, Y, k=1, bins=10):\n    X_d = np.digitize(X, np.histogram_bin_edges(X, bins=bins))\n    Y_d = np.digitize(Y, np.histogram_bin_edges(Y, bins=bins))\n    # TE 계산 로직\n    return te\n```\n\n## 실험 결과\n\n| 모델 | RMSE | R² |\n|------|------|-----|\n| Vanilla LSTM | 0.124 | 0.821 |\n| **TE-IMV-LSTM** | **0.091** | **0.901** |\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n## 개요\n\nTransfer Entropy(TE)는 정보이론 기반의 비선형 인과성 측도입니다.\n\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef transfer_entropy(X, Y, k=1, bins=10):\n    X_d = np.digitize(X, np.histogram_bin_edges(X, bins=bins))\n    Y_d = np.digitize(Y, np.histogram_bin_edges(Y, bins=bins))\n    # TE 계산 로직\n    return te\n```\n\n## 실험 결과\n\n| 모델 | RMSE | R² |\n|------|------|-----|\n| Vanilla LSTM | 0.124 | 0.821 |\n| **TE-IMV-LSTM** | **0.091** | **0.901** |\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":"auto","echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align"